    },
    {
      "end": 46.29999923706055,
      "text": "Be yourself, the untamed within A labyrinth of doubt that starts to spin",
      "start": 40.02000045776367
    },
    {
      "end": 51.7400016784668,
      "text": "In the depths of your soul A silent cry makes you grow",
      "start": 46.29999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 66,
      "text": "Cause fear is in us all You gotta work past it as you grow old",
