    },
    {
      "end": 171.8699951171875,
      "text": "All that matters how you deal with it",
      "start": 169.4499969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 177.91000366210938,
      "text": "For none of us can defy it The fear within",
      "start": 172.4499969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 185.25,
      "text": "And all that matters now Matters now is how you deal with it",
      "start": 179.4499969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 193.85000610351562,
      "text": "All this fear, all the sirens make me be fear All inside is this good time",
